        "To calculate the EV/EBITDA ratio, I need to retrieve the Enterprise Value (EV) and EBITDA for TotalEnergies SE. These values are typically available in the `tte.info` dictionary. After extracting them, I will compute the ratio and then consolidate all the fetched metrics into a single structure for easy access and display.\n",
